        "Description": "Greetings, 47.\r\rYour targets are controversial literature critic Marcello Schiavone and Catherine Lang, the manager of author Craig Black. Behind closed doors, the two have manipulated Sapienza locals through coercive seminars and subliminal messaging—indoctrinating them into a clandestine cult with dangerous intent. Both can be found around town during Black&apos;s recent novel reading at the local church. Eliminate them to dismantle their influence permanently.\r\rGood luck, 47.",
